title: Flying Star - Central Ave SE
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, International, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Mexican, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Regional chain run by people who support locavores and understand that people have varying dietary needs. Vegan, vegetarian, gluten-free and other alternatives are clearly marked on menu. The moove over meat veggie burgers are custom made for them. Try the buddha bowl.
